query: SELECT MIN(mi.info) AS movie_budget, MIN(mi_idx.info) AS movie_votes, MIN(n.name) AS writer, MIN(t.title) AS complete_gore_movie FROM complete_cast AS cc, comp_cast_type AS cct1, comp_cast_type AS cct2, cast_info AS ci, info_type AS it1, info_type AS it2, keyword AS k, movie_info AS mi, movie_info_idx AS mi_idx, movie_keyword AS mk, name AS n, title AS t WHERE t.id = mi.movie_id AND t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.id = ci.movie_id AND t.id = mk.movie_id AND t.id = cc.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND ci.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mi_idx.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = mk.movie_id AND mi_idx.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND mk.movie_id = cc.movie_id AND n.id = ci.person_id AND it1.id = mi.info_type_id AND it2.id = mi_idx.info_type_id AND k.id = mk.keyword_id AND cct1.id = cc.subject_id AND cct2.id = cc.status_id AND cct2.kind in ('cast','crew','complete') AND t.production_year > 1993 AND t.production_year < 2003 AND k.keyword not like '%justice%' AND k.keyword not like '%revengeful%' AND it2.info in ('LD disc format','LD number of chapter stops','LD length','opening weekend','essays','books','LD sharpness','LD master format','crazy credits','LD spaciality','LD audio quality','book','LD color rendition','screenplay-teleplay','printed media reviews','rating','trivia','LD additional information','sound mix','height','LD quality of source') AND cct1.kind in ('complete+verified','crew','complete') AND it1.info not in ('keywords','LD audio quality','bottom 10 rank','production process protocol','LD master format','portrayed in','LD video quality','LD additional information','LD supplement','LD catalog number','rating','birth date','birth name','LD group genre') AND mi_idx.info < '2.0' AND mi.info in ('Maori','Croatian','Japanese','Rotuman','German','Ladino','Galician','Dari','Slovenian','Swiss German','Cantonese','Faroese')
